---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MGEO Sports | Representación de Futbolistas | Agente FIFA">
  
  <section class="relative bg-brand-dark text-white min-h-[90vh] md:min-h-screen flex items-center px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/15 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl relative z-10 w-full">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-5 py-2 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-gray-300 font-body text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase font-bold">Agencia de Representación</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[6.5rem] font-heading font-bold leading-[1.05] mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Círculo cerrado <br />
        <span class="italic font-light text-gray-400">talento de élite<span class="text-brand-primary">.</span></span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mb-12 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-brand-primary pl-6">
        Scouting y selección exclusiva. No buscamos cantidad, gestionamos proyección. Representación estratégica integral bajo los más altos estándares internacionales de FIFA.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6">
        <a href="#talentos" class="bg-brand-primary text-white px-10 py-5 font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[11px] hover:bg-white hover:text-brand-dark transition-all duration-500 w-full sm:w-auto text-center shadow-[0_10px_30px_-10px_rgba(120,22,22,0.5)]">
          Ver Roster Oficial
        </a>
        <a href="#perfil-agente" class="text-white hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors font-body font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] group flex items-center justify-center gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto py-4">
          Perfil de Agencia <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="talentos" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#161616] text-white px-6 border-y border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none hidden md:block"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16 gap-6">
        <div>
          <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 block">Representación Oficial</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
            Talentos Exclusivos.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-2 hidden md:block">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/matias.georgetta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors font-body text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-3 border-b border-gray-700 hover:border-brand-primary pb-2 group">
            Ver firmas en Instagram
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-1 md:gap-2">
        
        <div class="md:col-span-8 md:row-span-2 group relative aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-auto md:h-[650px] bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden cursor-pointer md:rounded-sm">
          <img src="/elian-jugador.png" alt="Mira Acosta - Lanús" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top md:grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 scale-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-1000 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)]" />
          
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#161616] via-[#161616]/70 to-transparent opacity-90 md:group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-end items-start z-20">
            <span class="bg-brand-primary text-white px-3 py-1.5 text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase rounded-sm mb-4 inline-block">Defensor / 1ra División</span>
            <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">Mira Acosta</h3>
            <div class="w-12 h-px bg-white md:w-0 md:group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-700 ease-out mt-3 mb-3 md:mt-4 md:mb-4"></div>
            <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-medium text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Club Atlético Lanús</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 group relative aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-auto md:h-[321px] bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden cursor-pointer md:rounded-sm">
          <img src="/fede-jugador.png" alt="Federico Otero - Atlanta" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover md:grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 scale-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-1000 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)]" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#161616] via-[#161616]/70 to-transparent opacity-90 md:group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 md:p-8 items-start z-20 flex flex-col">
            <span class="bg-brand-primary text-white px-3 py-1 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase rounded-sm mb-3 inline-block">Volante / Cat. '04</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-1">Federico Otero</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white md:w-0 md:group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-700 ease-out my-3"></div>
            <p class="text-[10px] font-body font-medium text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Club Atlético Atlanta</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 group relative aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-auto md:h-[321px] bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden cursor-pointer md:rounded-sm">
          <img src="/ramiro-jugador.png" alt="Ramiro Amembi - Sportivo Italiano" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover md:grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 scale-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-1000 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)]" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#161616] via-[#161616]/70 to-transparent opacity-90 md:group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 md:p-8 items-start z-20 flex flex-col">
            <span class="bg-brand-primary text-white px-3 py-1 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase rounded-sm mb-3 inline-block">Delantero / Cat. '05</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-1">Ramiro Amembi</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white md:w-0 md:group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-700 ease-out my-3"></div>
            <p class="text-[10px] font-body font-medium text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Sportivo Italiano</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-6 md:row-span-1 group relative aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-auto md:h-[350px] bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden cursor-pointer md:rounded-sm">
          <img src="/matias-jugador.png" alt="Matías Lucero - Arsenal" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top md:grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 scale-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-1000 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)]" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#161616] via-[#161616]/70 to-transparent opacity-90 md:group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 md:p-8 items-start z-20 flex flex-col">
            <span class="bg-brand-primary text-white px-3 py-1.5 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase rounded-sm mb-3 inline-block">Volante / Cat. '03</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-1">Matías Lucero</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white md:w-0 md:group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-700 ease-out my-3"></div>
            <p class="text-[10px] font-body font-medium text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Arsenal de Sarandí</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-6 md:row-span-1 bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center md:rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-primary/10 blur-[40px]"></div>
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-primary mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" /></svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-3">Admisión Cerrada</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            MGEO Sports opera exclusivamente mediante el scouting interno y selección directa de nuestra red de ojeadores. No recibimos ni evaluamos perfiles por canales públicos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:hidden flex justify-center py-8">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/matias.georgetta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white bg-brand-primary px-8 py-4 font-body text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold flex items-center gap-3">
            Ver redes oficiales
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="perfil-agente" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white px-6 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative order-2 lg:order-1 mt-10 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm relative z-10 shadow-2xl">
            <img src="/matias-geo.png" alt="Matías Georgetta - Agente FIFA" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark/10 hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-full h-full border-2 border-brand-primary/20 z-0 rounded-sm hidden md:block"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 block">Director & Agente</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Matías Georgetta<br/>
            <span class="italic font-light text-gray-400">Agente Oficial.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 font-light text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
            MGEO Sports fusiona el conocimiento exhaustivo del marco legal con la pasión por el fútbol. Al estar respaldados por nuestra propia firma jurídica, garantizamos que la carrera de nuestros seleccionados esté protegida, blindada y optimizada.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#F9F8F6] p-4 rounded-sm border border-gray-100 w-full sm:w-auto shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-dark text-brand-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-primary leading-tight">Credencial Oficial</span>
                <p class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark text-xl">Licencia FIFA ID 202305-1916</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <a href="https://instagram.com/matias.georgetta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm font-body font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 0C5.829 0 5.556.01 4.703.048 3.85.088 3.269.222 2.76.42a3.917 3.917 0 0 0-1.417.923A3.927 3.927 0 0 0 .42 2.76C.222 3.268.087 3.85.048 4.7.01 5.555 0 5.827 0 8.001c0 2.172.01 2.444.048 3.297.04.852.174 1.433.372 1.942.205.526.478.972.923 1.417.444.445.89.719 1.416.923.51.198 1.09.333 1.942.372C5.555 15.99 5.827 16 8 16s2.444-.01 3.298-.048c.851-.04 1.434-.174 1.943-.372a3.916 3.916 0 0 0 1.416-.923c.445-.445.718-.891.923-1.417.197-.509.332-1.09.372-1.942C15.99 10.445 16 10.173 16 8s-.01-2.445-.048-3.299c-.04-.851-.175-1.433-.372-1.941a3.926 3.926 0 0 0-.923-1.417A3.911 3.911 0 0 0 13.24.42c-.51-.198-1.092-.333-1.943-.372C10.443.01 10.172 0 7.998 0h.003zm-.717 1.442h.718c2.136 0 2.389.007 3.232.046.78.036 1.204.166 1.486.275.373.145.64.319.92.599.28.28.453.546.598.92.11.281.24.705.275 1.485.039.843.047 1.096.047 3.231s-.008 2.389-.047 3.232c-.035.78-.166 1.203-.275 1.485a2.47 2.47 0 0 1-.599.919c-.28.28-.546.453-.92.598-.28.11-.704.24-1.485.276-.843.038-1.096.047-3.232.047s-2.39-.009-3.233-.047c-.78-.036-1.203-.166-1.485-.276a2.478 2.478 0 0 1-.92-.598 2.48 2.48 0 0 1-.6-.92c-.109-.281-.24-.705-.275-1.485-.038-.843-.046-1.096-.046-3.233 0-2.136.008-2.388.046-3.231.036-.78.166-1.204.276-1.486.145-.373.319-.64.599-.92.28-.28.546-.453.92-.598.282-.11.705-.24 1.485-.276.738-.034 1.024-.044 2.515-.045v.002zm4.988 1.328a.96.96 0 1 0 0 1.92.96.96 0 0 0 0-1.92zm-4.27 1.122a4.109 4.109 0 1 0 0 8.217 4.109 4.109 0 0 0 0-8.217zm0 1.441a2.667 2.667 0 1 1 0 5.334 2.667 2.667 0 0 1 0-5.334z"/></svg>
              @matias.georgetta
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 border border-brand-dark shadow-xl">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">Proyección Global</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-light leading-relaxed">Conexiones directas y licencia oficial para negociar en todo el mundo sin intermediarios.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="servicios-sports" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#F9F8F6] px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs mb-4 block">Nuestra Infraestructura</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-tight">Gestión Deportiva.</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-light text-lg mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Nuestros representados acceden a una estructura de protección y desarrollo que cubre todas sus necesidades profesionales.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        
        <div class="bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-gray-100 flex flex-col xl:flex-row overflow-hidden">
          <div class="xl:w-5/12 bg-brand-dark text-white p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">Intermediación y <br/><span class="text-brand-primary italic">Transferencias</span></h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Gestión operativa y legal de contratos laborales con clubes a nivel nacional e internacional.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="xl:w-7/12 p-10 md:p-14 bg-white flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-brand-dark font-bold font-heading text-lg mb-2">Para Futbolistas</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">Búsqueda de oportunidades de mercado, negociación de salarios, primas, bonos por objetivos y condiciones de traspaso.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-brand-dark font-bold font-heading text-lg mb-2">Para Clubes</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">Mandatos oficiales para scouting, colocación de jugadores y estructuración de operaciones de compra/venta o cesión.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-gray-100 flex flex-col xl:flex-row-reverse overflow-hidden">
          <div class="xl:w-5/12 bg-[#161616] text-white p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">Asesoramiento <br/><span class="text-brand-primary italic">Legal y Financiero</span></h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                El respaldo directo del Estudio Jurídico MGEO aplicado a la carrera del deportista.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="xl:w-7/12 p-10 md:p-14 bg-white">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 rounded-sm bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                  <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold mt-1">01</span>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-1">Derechos de Formación y Solidaridad</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-light">Gestión y reclamo ante FIFA por derechos formativos para clubes y academias.</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 rounded-sm bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                  <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold mt-1">02</span>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-1">Conflictos Contractuales</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-light">Defensa en tribunales ordinarios o cámara de resolución de disputas (TAS/CAS).</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 rounded-sm bg-gray-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                  <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold mt-1">03</span>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-1">Planificación Patrimonial</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-light">Estructuración fiscal e inversiones para asegurar el futuro económico post-retiro.</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-brand-primary/20 flex flex-col xl:flex-row overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-brand-primary"></div>
          <div class="xl:w-5/12 bg-brand-dark text-white p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">Desarrollo de <br/><span class="text-brand-primary italic">Imagen y Sponsoreo</span></h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
                El futbolista actual es una marca. Gestionamos acuerdos comerciales y presencia digital para maximizar los ingresos extra-deportivos.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="xl:w-7/12 p-10 md:p-14 bg-white flex items-center">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 w-full">
               <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-primary pl-4">
